sentences: Geert Huinink (Dutch pronunciation: [ˈɣeːrt ˈɦœynɪŋk]) (born 29 April 1971) is a Dutch electronic music producer and classical composer.
Geert has also produced for a Dutch television show called "Meiden van de Wit" in 2002.
The Dawnseekers is one of the aliases used by Geert, along with Alco Lammers, that produced melodic and uplifting trance tracks during the early 2000s.
